<H4>3</H4></TD><TD><P>Wherefore are we counted as beasts, and reputed vile in   
your sight?</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V4><H4>4</H4></TD><TD><P>He 
teareth himself in his anger: shall the earth be forsaken for thee? and shall   
